# Snapshots Directory

This directory stores test output snapshots for comparison.

## Structure

- `*_master.log` - Master/reference snapshots (commit these to git)
- `*_YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS.log` - Timestamped test run snapshots (temporary, not committed)

## Usage

Initialize master snapshots:
```bash
../judge.sh setup
```

Compare tests against master snapshots:
```bash
../judge.sh run
```

Update master snapshots:
```bash
../judge.sh run -u
```
